Body:
assert bodyfat.GenericCalculator(age, sex, skinfolds).log_sum == pytest.approx(
    expected, rel=0.01)
pytest.mark.parametrize('age,sex,skinfolds,expected', [(30, 'male', (1, 2, 
    3), 0.78), (20, 'female', (1, 2, 3, 4), 1), (45, 'Male', (1, 2), 0.48),
    (50, 'FEMALE', (1, 2, 3, 4, 5), 1.17)])
